    "This process can be applied at various levels of granularity, such as token, sentence, and semantic levels.• Token-level Chunking is straightforward but may split sentences, affecting retrieval quality.• Semantic-level Chunking uses LLMs to determine breakpoints, context-preserving but timeconsuming.",
    "• Sentence-level Chunking balances preserving text semantics with simplicity and efficiency.In this study, we use sentence-level chunking, balancing simplicity and semantic preservation.",
